com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.login

Interface LoginRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LoginMsg, MsgBase

    public interface LoginRequest
extends LoginMsg
    The RDM login request. Used by an OMM Consumer or OMM Non-Interactive Provider to request a login.
    See Also:
    MsgBase, LoginMsg
